Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by special guest SERE Specialist Tiffany Hart as they discuss a woman that Dan knew called the "Dual Exhaust", we create a new new game show involving 3 to 4 large thick ropes, the "extreme sex" porn that's going around the internet, how the fountain of youth is only a generation away, the bold choice to get hair plugs if you're a dude, Tiffany chats about a guy she dated who couldn't get it up, what the proper rules are for bringing and leaving booze at a party, and the depressing end to "Growing Pains" legend Richard T. Stabone.
